Privacy Policy for Guruhelper
Last updated: April 9, 2026
Guruhelper ("we", "us", or "our") operates the Guruhelper mobile application (the "App"). This Privacy Policy describes how we collect, use, and protect your personal information.
1. Information We Collect
We collect the following types of information:
- Account Information: Name and email address when you register or sign in using email, Google, or Apple.
- User Content: Photos, images, and audio recordings that you attach to your tasks and schedules.
- User Identifiers: A unique user ID is generated for your account.
- Device Information: Push notification tokens to send you task notifications.
2. How We Use Your Information
We use your information for the following purposes:
- To provide and maintain the app functionality (scheduling, task management)
- To authenticate your identity and secure your account
- To send push notifications about your tasks and team activities
- To enable team collaboration features
3. Data Storage and Security
Your data is stored securely using Google Firebase services including Firebase Authentication, Cloud Firestore, and Firebase Cloud Storage. All data is transmitted using industry-standard encryption (HTTPS/TLS).
4. Data Sharing
We do not sell, trade, or share your personal information with third parties. Your data is only shared within your team if you choose to join or create a team within the app.
5. Third-Party Services
The app uses Google Firebase for authentication, database, and file storage. The app also uses Google Sign-In and Apple Sign-In for optional account authentication.
6. Your Rights
You have the right to access your personal data, request deletion of your account, and update your personal information through the app profile settings.
7. Data Retention
Your data is retained as long as your account is active. If you delete your account, your personal data will be removed within 30 days.
8. Children Privacy
Our app is not intended for children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13.
9. Changes to This Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page.
